Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================Pre===================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.62,0:00:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.15,0:00:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱纪同学 有纪同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.75,0:00:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美佐枝今天请假哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.04,0:00:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上给纱纪打了电话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.37,0:00:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是因为感冒 今天不来学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.72,0:00:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.01,0:00:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美佐枝会不到校 很不寻常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.28,0:00:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是被五十岚君…这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…被甩了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.21,0:00:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美佐枝好可怜…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.14,0:00:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是志麻君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.44,0:00:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们觉得比起五十岚君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.51,0:00:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样的孩子和美佐枝更配哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好安慰美佐枝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.35,0:00:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会把她叫到公园去的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================OP===================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.94,0:01:18.37,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}熟悉的坡道上 却已不见你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:24.05,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}柔和的阳光 透过树叶投下斑点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.13,0:01:29.28,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}我独自一人 伫立在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.32,0:01:36.59,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}回顾着那些 温暖的往事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.09,0:01:44.71,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}只有你 只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.78,0:01:50.78,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}在变幻的时间中 永驻我心底
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:58.55,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}风吹而过 泪水渗眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.66,0:02:05.59,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}你的身影 已变得更远
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.66,0:02:07.70,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}任何时候都不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.70,0:02:09.87,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}哪怕一切的一切全部改变
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.87,0:02:12.08,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}不忘记那一件 那一件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.08,0:02:14.46,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}稀松平常之事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.49,0:02:15.57,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}终会让你看到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:18.79,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}那被光芒包裹着的唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:20.85,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}守护 守护
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.85,0:02:23.89,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)\be1}直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================Text===================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.37,0:02:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相乐同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻君…你怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 相乐同…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:02:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 美佐枝同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.26,0:03:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.42,0:03:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱就像遥远往昔燃起的烟火呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.23,0:03:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪耀后散落愈显美丽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来找打的么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:13.96,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 用这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又没有哭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就在上厕所忘带纸时…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这算是为人着想还是神经大条啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老说奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.53,0:03:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都是有纪和纱纪教的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.47,0:03:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看出来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己不可能说这种话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说就用自己的话说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.39,0:03:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.61,0:03:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.84,0:03:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…我肯定有什么不对的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不对的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.29,0:04:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起来 貌似有很多…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢 我现在消沉是因为别的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非想 现在是「是拿下美佐枝的机会」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我昨天说的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那种想法…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.07,0:04:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是来向我报恩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也并不是喜欢我之类呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是…喜欢我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:05:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…喜欢我的哪方面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会训斥鞭策人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.97,0:05:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会为人担心着想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 被施展格斗技时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会闻到美佐枝同学好闻的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后那条就用不着了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.67,0:05:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 不用道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.61,0:05:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美佐枝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说在车站对面新开了一家冰淇淋店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 今天…看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.01,0:06:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人专程等着 不陪着他太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.53,0:06:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像进展得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满脸的高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会长？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看我这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是本校首位女性学生会长哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美佐枝同学好厉害啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋祭在即了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们学校也会协助举办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在有点忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋祭？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 如果没别的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.27,0:06:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要…和我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.73,0:06:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看秋祭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 绝对会被拆穿吧 这种样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 很合适的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 美佐枝同学很忙吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好像是有学生会的会议
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我们转告 会晚些放
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看看美佐枝同学工作的样子呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说…可爱得让人气恼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:17.35,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将这份爱 悄悄献给你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:19.09,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ROCK&ROCK&ROLL…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是芳野学长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是那么有人气呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你是哪个班的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.03,0:07:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没见过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚转来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要带你在学校转转
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这孩子有我们跟着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.21,0:07:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不用费心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是搭讪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.47,0:07:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻君 快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:43.57,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那告诉我你的名字和班级吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么下一个议题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于带吉他过来喧闹的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌是随他便 但是在教室吵闹就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来学生会室有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事可以直接进去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有规定禁止入内
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.73,0:08:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这个 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相乐同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊吹老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.84,0:08:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉打断会议了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.74,0:08:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像有话要说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.89,0:08:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本校原来有这么可爱的女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.29,0:08:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢…您
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话要说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请随便说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会的工作就是听取学生的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请继续…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的话…请继续陪在我身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:08:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.11,0:09:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们之间是怎样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的超有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.19,0:09:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有被看穿呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.77,0:09:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.34,0:09:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定美佐枝会更中意这打扮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘记了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 志麻君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你接下来有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我们两个在商量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就想去你家玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…美佐枝还没去过你家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先于女友踏进少年家中的优越感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:10:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 然后向美佐枝炫耀一番吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不方便招待吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家在哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想不起来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 不就在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开奇怪的玩笑啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.10,0:10:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.37,0:10:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 说声「我回来了」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.65,0:10:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是贺津纪的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还真是…让你们费心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进来吧 给贺津纪上柱香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:11:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的志麻贺津纪 已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我并不是志麻贺津纪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.53,0:11:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.28,0:11:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么缘由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我们能帮得上的忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 只希望你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为对我们来说 你就是志麻君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生什么 我们都是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事会对美佐枝保密的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什么必须说的话 要亲口对她说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是志麻贺津纪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那曾是我心目中最重要的人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起度过了很长很长的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.07,0:12:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人将最后的愿望托付给了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为实现那个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.43,0:12:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来迟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时都是我让你久等呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天那女孩 是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.45,0:12:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然被看穿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然看得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们每天都见面的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 反正那也是有纪和纱纪指使的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.80,0:13:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为此而出现的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 这里面有能实现愿望的「光」…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就没有东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然 就是现在的我不需要它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为重要的 是现在的我们过得幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.93,0:13:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这个也很重要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.57,0:13:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就公布让志麻君久等的愿望了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.78,0:13:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远地喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请永远 永远地 继续喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 吓着你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是喜欢这个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然短暂 但一起度过的时间弥足珍贵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也喜欢有纪同学和纱纪同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.59,0:14:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢…四个人一起度过的时光了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是学你昨天说过的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.95,0:15:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…为什么要哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人放不下心的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美佐枝同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…真的非常谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我去买点喝的过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里等会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻君？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:15:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见…美佐枝同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一生…都喜欢着你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到…永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.01,0:16:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 男生宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还没那打算
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.26,0:16:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是因为忘不了他啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能这就是我的人生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有机会三人碰个面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.65,0:17:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也叫上有纪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.05,0:17:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是赖在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么想留在我身边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是特别喜欢猫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真傻 我在想什么童话一样的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是只奇怪的猫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也君 朋也君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.57,0:17:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得真香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我家的猫一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经很晚了 我们告辞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 弄的这么晚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 记得让他带你去秋祭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.13,0:18:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你让我做的梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明有名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事要向她传达是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 朋也君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从昨晚起就一直在想着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想着该怎么跟美佐枝小姐说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美佐枝小姐的猫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 还有话要说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.66,0:18:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古河同学 还有她男友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美佐枝小姐 晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 帮我抓住它了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.69,0:18:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喘不过气来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它无所谓 能不能换个称呼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.72,0:19:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美佐枝小姐和小猫一起来逛祭典吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 它突然跑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果一路追到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 真是让人放不下心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.25,0:19:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.92,0:19:31.32,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…要回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它一定…早就想和美佐枝小姐来这祭典了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天 我好像在梦里听见了它的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.17,0:19:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说「祭典时没能陪到最后 对不起」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有吗 没说什么别的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:19:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有「如你所愿 一直就在你身旁」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不记得 和猫有过约会的约定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天 就陪你玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美佐枝小姐 还有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.79,0:20:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它希望美佐枝小姐能幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 它就是这样的家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.36,0:20:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它担心着美佐枝小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.51,0:20:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.23,0:20:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也试着再青春一回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.11,0:20:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会和你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于昨晚的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:21:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一场很久以前的 不可思议的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的主人不再是你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.66,0:21:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也是个很温柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.87,0:21:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 时而会不安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有没有实现目标呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.86,0:21:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有…完成和你的约定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些事…已消逝在记忆的深处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 现在就想这样度过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.90,0:21:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅这样的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.99,0:22:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我永远…永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.90,0:22:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在她身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================ED===================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:26.07,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}双眼凝视着 流动的云朵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:32.99,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}心中感受着 天空变幻的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.74,0:22:41.18,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}伫立不前的我们 察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.32,0:22:48.20,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}这变迁的世界编织出的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.32,0:22:55.44,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}伸出的指尖 不断寻找着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.44,0:23:04.13,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}那恒久不变的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.35,0:23:11.69,ed2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}举起的手中火炬闪亮
